2. GoodsController – Get Goods by ID (GET)

Endpoint: GET /api/goods/{id}

{
  "id": 1,
  "name": "Laptop",
  "quantity": 50,
  "unitOfMeasure": "Piece",
  "location": "Warehouse 1",
  "expiryDate": "2025-12-31",
